Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw watched the fighting go one from below. She watched as the 
majority of them attacked Dinobot. But she didn't care. She never backed 
anyone up. It was her life she was defending. She watched as a wounded bot, 
Serpentor limped off to a tree.

Her lips went into a sneer. He was perfect; she didn't need to risk herself 
in high intense of battle. She down to him, and grabbed him by the 
shoulders, lifting him up into the air.

"I believe you and I have to talk," she said. "Predacon to Predacon." She 
went to fly him away from the battle field.
